{
  "chapter": 41,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十一回 杀机四伏：小方与阳光在木屋中被神秘高手围困，多次尝试突围均被逼回。卜鹰现身引开埋伏，二人趁机脱身，但最终仍选择追随卜鹰。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "今天的天气真不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "的确不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你想不想出去走走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不想去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你去，我在这里等你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "好！我一个人去。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "林木后人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "回去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我回来得快不快？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "真是快极了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "林木后人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这条路也走不通，你还是得回去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "时候已经不早了，一天过得真快。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你还想不想出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那么我们不如还是早点睡吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我睡床，你也睡床。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你受伤没有？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果他们想呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "那么我现在已经是个死人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不管怎么样，反正他们暂时还不会出手的，我们不妨先睡一下再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我们不能睡。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "因为我们不能留在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你想冲出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我们一定要冲出去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是你已经试过。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我们很可能连一成机会都没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那么我们无非是送死。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "就算要死，我们也得冲出去。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "因为我们绝不能连累卜鹰。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "他很可能还留在附近，这些人既不出手，又不放我们走，为的就是要利用我们诱卜鹰入伏，如果卜鹰还在附近，他会不会让我们被困死在这里？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我们能不能让他来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果你决心要这么做，我们就这么做。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不管你要到哪里去，我都跟着你，你要下地狱，我也下地狱。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们好像有客人来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们不理他行不行？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "为什么不理他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他连门都不敲就闯进来，连一点礼貌都没有，这种人理他干什么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗林中人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然来了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗林中人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下既然已经来了，为什么不出来跟大家见见面？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗林中人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这里！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗林中人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓卜的，你还想往哪里走？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗林中人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就留下命来吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "他在哪里，我就到哪里去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    }
